{"tid":1653200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚惠珠：提議設暴亂特別法庭　彭定康靠香港話題刷存在感","createTime":"2019-10-14T03:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T04:49:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cd75db9889423ca9d494dbb37306e295c5bc29b9","tid":1653200,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠表示，《禁止蒙面規例》是止暴制亂的一把利器，有助於警方執法。她又說，過去4個多月，警方拘捕很多人，法庭積壓大量案件，需要排期審理，認為香港可以借鑑外國一些做法，例如成立「暴亂特別法庭」，專門審理這段時間的案件。<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠接受內地傳媒專訪，據新華社的報道，她回應訂立《禁止蒙面規例》是否違法時表示，人大常委會在香港回歸前，已通過決議決定吸收《緊急情況規例條例》，成為香港特區的法律。<br />\n<br />\n在回歸後，有關法律的約束力亦經過特區的立法機關確認，根據有關條例，行政長官會同行政會議在香港出現屬緊急或危害公安的情況下，可訂立任何認為合乎公眾利益的規例。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，有關規例屬於先訂立、後審議的附屬法例，相信在立法會復會後，有理智、負責任的議員都會支援，法例一定能獲得通過。<br />\n<br />\n另外，對於前港督彭定康接受英國傳媒訪問時，形容特區政府制訂《禁止蒙面規例》是瘋狂之舉，譚惠珠認為，證明彭定康在英國已是過氣政客，需要靠香港話題刷存在感，又指英國早已訂立反蒙面法，應對抗議示威和騷亂，批評彭定康的說法是典型的雙重標準。"},{"pid":"0c6c2452d0580f0181e892c5b8eeabbd0b1de7fa","tid":1653200,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486031-20191014.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486031-20191014.htm&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=743e0486\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486031-20191014.htm&h=b5c8d3d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486031-20191014.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2224a69161acb1bb7813bc4484d6ff8a6451172f","tid":1653200,"uid":23672,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"彭定康: 譚惠珠靠戇鳩刷存在感"},{"pid":"c19234fc05c5ae8801b1732a40d12ba46486cd2a","tid":1653200,"uid":14422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"證明彭定康在英國已是過氣政客<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠就唔撚過氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6faf46a13bb8a84f3a3d5b62b39a0e382d176e","tid":1653200,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:40:49.000Z","msg":"講還講"},{"pid":"a116e24e43ec146b3179cd788eaffb8a252805a0","tid":1653200,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2224a69161acb1bb7813bc4484d6ff8a6451172f","tid":1653200,"uid":23672,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"彭定康: 譚惠珠靠戇鳩刷存在感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:41:00.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n［第九期牆紙］四色分類，你我做到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1647496/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1647496/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=1dbbb5d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n歡迎投稿 : <a href=\"https://padlet.com/lennonnewshk/6g5yp3tllkxx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpadlet.com%2Flennonnewshk%2F6g5yp3tllkxx&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=910c97d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://padlet.com/lennonnewshk/6g5yp3tllkxx</a>"},{"pid":"90b58b580d4f49c83362fbb0346bb546b30cacc3","tid":1653200,"uid":119478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"人地係北愛成功修復警民關係使唔使講香港黎提升存在感呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9de18f356f68958ab353454edcddb5ac690cdc","tid":1653200,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:44:22.000Z","msg":"我淨係見到有隻豬刷存在感<br />\n人地有實績，呢條豬閪為香港做過d咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實點解成日要訪問一個豬閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6da32f414f6022b8a2be4841f6e6706af97e26","tid":1653200,"uid":254504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:46:19.00